query:
UPDATE merchandise_items SET imageUrl = CASE 
  WHEN type = 'uniform' THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555597673-b21d5c935865?w=400&h=400&fit=crop'
  WHEN type = 'belt' THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544367567-0f2fcb009e0b?w=400&h=400&fit=crop'
  WHEN type = 'gear' THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517438322307-e67111335449?w=400&h=400&fit=crop'
  ELSE 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517438322307-e67111335449?w=400&h=400&fit=crop'
END
WHERE imageUrl IS NULL;
